ca.ualberta.trinkettrader.Friends.TrackedFriends

Class TrackedFriendsListActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • ca.ualberta.trinkettrader.Friends.TrackedFriends.TrackedFriendsListActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer

    public class TrackedFriendsListActivity
extends Activity
implements java.util.Observer
    Android activity class for displaying a user's tracked friendslist. From this activity all of the user's tracked friends can be viewed in the tracked friends list. This activity contains a "Go Back" button which will connect the user to the FriendsListActivity. Clicking on a friend within the friends list will connect the user to the FriendsProfileActivity, which will allow the user to view the details of that friend, and choose whether to untrack the friend, or to remove them.
